strings.Value: "If my own servants were so careless in setting camp..."
"You can't even conceal a camp. What good are you at all, then?"
"She deliberately taunts you. Pay her no heed."
"When this is over, I'll twist your head off. If I can wait that long."
"There are no servants and no masters here, damn it all! If you want something, you can do it yourself."
"Oh, one day I will just walk up to that arrogant, snobbish waif and give her SUCH a slap upside her head..."
"Do you still dream of the days when you had servants?"
